public class MyFitnessFunction
extends FitnessFunction

Sample Fitness function (Rastrigin's function) f( x1 , x2 ) = 20.0 + (x1 * x1) + (x2 * x2) - 10.0 * (Math.cos(2 * Math.PI * x1) + Math.cos(2 * Math.PI * x2));
